@startuml sequence_telemetry_ingestion
!theme plain
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title Telemetry Ingestion - Happy Path + Retry + Dead Letter

participant "IoT Device" as IoT
participant "TelemetryIngestionFunction" as Func
participant "DapperTelemetryRepository" as Repo
database "SQL Server" as DB
participant "DeadLetterService" as DL
participant "AlertEvaluatorService" as Alert

== Happy Path ==

IoT -> Func: POST /api/telemetry\nX-Api-Key: <configured-key>\n{ equipmentId, payload... }

Func -> Func: Validate API key\n(no hardcoded fallback)
Func -> Func: Deserialize & validate payload

Func -> Repo: InsertAsync(event)
Repo -> DB: Dapper INSERT TelemetryEvents\n(attempt 1)
DB --> Repo: success
Repo --> Func: eventId

Func -> Alert: EvaluateAsync(event)
note right: Fire-and-forget\n(does not block response)

Func --> IoT: **202 Accepted**\n{ eventId: "guid", status: "accepted" }

== Transient Failure with Retry ==

IoT -> Func: POST /api/telemetry
Func -> Repo: InsertAsync(event)

Repo -> DB: Dapper INSERT (attempt 1)
DB --> Repo: SqlException (transient)

Repo -> Repo: Wait 1000ms
Repo -> DB: Dapper INSERT (attempt 2)
DB --> Repo: SqlException (transient)

Repo -> Repo: Wait 4000ms
Repo -> DB: Dapper INSERT (attempt 3)
DB --> Repo: success
Repo --> Func: eventId

Func --> IoT: 202 Accepted

== Permanent Failure -> Dead Letter ==

IoT -> Func: POST /api/telemetry
Func -> Repo: InsertAsync(event)

Repo -> DB: attempt 1 - FAIL
Repo -> DB: attempt 2 - FAIL
Repo -> DB: attempt 3 - FAIL
Repo --> Func: TelemetryInsertFailedException

Func -> DL: EnqueueAsync(event, error)
DL -> DB: INSERT TelemetryDeadLetterQueue
DB --> DL: stored

Func --> IoT: **202 Accepted**\n(event accepted for processing)

@enduml
